{"tid":1985553,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"全港最大良心飯券計劃正式上線啦！","createTime":"2020-04-23T08:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T10:47:07.000Z","uid":298736,"like":57,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"66ddf45ac0c0b75708ecf0677d733fa064353373","tid":1985553,"uid":298736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T08:19:48.000Z","msg":"傑斯出左個良心飯券計劃 詳情睇link<br />\n<br />\n簡單講就係手足用貼紙入黄店食野<br />\n黄店痴張單/貼紙落塊版<br />\n你得閒就去間黄店消費 順便清左張單 1張又得 清晒全版又得 睇自己能力<br />\n<br />\n手足有飯開 黄店有生意<br />\n家長唔洗煩惱 細路唔洗take risk揾家長<br />\n<br />\n利申 唔係絕對認同傑斯同慢必 3點維權 D睇法 但試過唔同方法幫手足開飯睇醫生 都覺得毫無效率 難得有人line up飯券計劃 值得一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbetween1 傑斯有捐錢幫手足 避難台灣都有出力<br />\nbetween2 如果唔信都可以睇下hokoguide有另外既飯券計劃<br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/901362236584137/posts/2812263218827353/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F901362236584137%2Fposts%2F2812263218827353%2F&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6r7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=0cb1332d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/901362236584137/posts/2812263218827353/</a><br />\n<br />\n參與黄店：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/14eZg3bM89oCGYFfmjArmHEmknCyCvlLKkDmxwlUf9Os/htmlview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F14eZg3bM89oCGYFfmjArmHEmknCyCvlLKkDmxwlUf9Os%2Fhtmlview&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6r7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=fdcc2aeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/14eZg3bM89oCGYFfmjArmHEmknCyCvlLKkDmxwlUf9Os/htmlview</a>"},{"pid":"8bbe6f036b06bdb45b5dc450489fce1218ae1bc0","tid":1985553,"uid":192296,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66ddf45ac0c0b75708ecf0677d733fa064353373","tid":1985553,"uid":298736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T08:19:48.000Z","msg":"傑斯出左個良心飯券計劃 詳情睇link<br />\n<br />\n簡單講就係手足用貼紙入黄店食野<br />\n黄店痴張單/貼紙落塊版<br />\n你得閒就去間黄店消費 順便清左張單 1張又得 清晒全版又得 睇自己能力<br />\n<br />\n手足有飯開 黄店有生意<br />\n家長唔洗煩惱 細路唔洗take risk揾家長<br />\n<br />\n利申 唔係絕對認同傑斯同慢必 3點維權 D睇法 但試過唔同方法幫手足開飯睇醫生 都覺得毫無效率 難得有人line up飯券計劃 值得一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbetween1 傑斯有捐錢幫手足 避難台灣都有出力<br />\nbetween2 如果唔信都可以睇下hokoguide有另外既飯券計劃<br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/901362236584137/posts/2812263218827353/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F901362236584137%2Fposts%2F2812263218827353%2F&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6r7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=0cb1332d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/901362236584137/posts/2812263218827353/</a><br />\n<br />\n參與黄店：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/14eZg3bM89oCGYFfmjArmHEmknCyCvlLKkDmxwlUf9Os/htmlview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F14eZg3bM89oCGYFfmjArmHEmknCyCvlLKkDmxwlUf9Os%2Fhtmlview&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6r7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=fdcc2aeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/14eZg3bM89oCGYFfmjArmHEmknCyCvlLKkDmxwlUf9Os/htmlview</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T08:36:15.000Z","msg":"推啊!!!!!"},{"pid":"56b1b9c64f4101330051d2ec9adee5532094b25a","tid":1985553,"uid":280475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T08:40:13.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"9aa783cc13cb6a91406a0a1c2ea0076b15d1a7d4","tid":1985553,"uid":5005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T15:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a807e619ae0dc6962075c65383a8332952a6f3c8","tid":1985553,"uid":70771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T15:58:52.000Z","msg":"推, 襯而家搞起佢, 做好個勢, 到時疫情減退可以開波果陣就幫到好多手足"},{"pi